{"tid":1134643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命考試】印一周內21學生因不及格輕生 調查卻揭電腦評分系統出錯","createTime":"2019-05-01T22:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T07:12:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6410a023729c31eaed4771adc371ad160ab6643","tid":1134643,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:20:51.000Z","msg":"印度南部泰倫加納邦（Telangana）過去一周最少有21名學生因不滿意考試成績而自殺，然而報道指可能是新的電腦評分系統出錯，才令考生以為自己不及格。政府承認新系統存在「重大缺陷」，加上有可能涉及人為錯誤，承諾會徹查事件。<br />\n今次的考試共有100萬名學生參與，成績在本月18日公佈，結果共有30萬名學生不合格。有去年表現優異的學生，在今年的分數只得個位數字。<br />\n政府官員承認新電腦評分系統存「重大缺陷」，事件亦牽涉人為錯誤。數以百計的學生和家長上街遊行表達不滿，有家長說：「我的兒子在首年考試中名列前茅，但現在他的分數是個位數，我不知該怎樣做。我向他保證問題必定會解決，但如果他傷害自己怎麼辦？」<br />\n政客請求學生不要傷害自己，稱會提供免費覆核。但據報本來負責改卷的一間私人機構也會參與覆核，令不少人擔心。泰倫加納邦首長拉奧（Chandrashekhar Rao）說：「考試不及格不等於生命失敗。生命誠可貴，即使不及格，將來也會有很多機會。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190430/large/1556630456_cd84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190430%2Flarge%2F1556630456_cd84.jpg&h=09a96ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190501/59546169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190501%2F59546169&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=07114162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190501%2F59546169&h=16d6bb64\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190501/59546169</a>"},{"pid":"0a37af2cbf830806116c19bfdd222b6f7374b225","tid":1134643,"uid":50801,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「考試不及格不等於生命失敗。生命誠可貴，即使不及格，將來也會有很多機會。」</blockquote><br />\n風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bf0592fd3e683f815d7f87850c799ccf212892","tid":1134643,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:37:33.000Z","msg":"3idiots"},{"pid":"04022b4571907a0d77db693a30d5dd23867aca75","tid":1134643,"uid":29382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:39:57.000Z","msg":"係咪同d有錢仔調轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07891aef06566fa8b9ec9e7fb106ea964051ed6","tid":1134643,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a37af2cbf830806116c19bfdd222b6f7374b225","tid":1134643,"uid":50801,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「考試不及格不等於生命失敗。生命誠可貴，即使不及格，將來也會有很多機會。」</blockquote><br />\n風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:44:13.000Z","msg":"雖然考生係承受好多壓力 但其實佢講得錯唔曬嘅 印度咁多人 你考得好都唔代表爭得贏 加埋種姓制度+父幹 考試真係未必幫到好多 做人都係睇開啲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cca4ba872532b58669af3a6e6b276620b256286","tid":1134643,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:31:27.000Z","msg":"印度IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1967ffff44f9720a8e6429fbaf0671f851b9dd39","tid":1134643,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.probytes.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.probytes.net%2Fwp-content%2Fupl